FT  28 NOV 94 / UK Company News: American Opportunity
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
American Opportunity Trust had net assets of Pounds 16.8m at the end of the
year to September 30. This represented a rise of 18 per cent on last year's
Pounds 14.2m, and compared with a 4 per cent fall in Standard &amp; Poor's
