Fully diluted net assets per share were 139.5p (121.6p).
Net deficit for the year widened to Pounds 89,000 (Pounds 77,000), with
losses per share of 1.18p (1.02p) and no dividend recommended.
The Hambro-managed trust changed its name from Leveraged Opportunity Trust.
