</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P6231 Security and Commodity Exchanges.
    P6726 Investment Offices, NEC.
</IN>
<XX>
Types:-
</XX>
<TP>FIN  Share issues.
    COSTS  Equity prices.
    CMMT  Comment &amp; Analysis.
</TP>
<PUB>The Financial Times
</PUB>
